**Solution:** 
- Load metadata from `lineitem_metadata.txt` to discover column file locations and dictionary encodings
- Use `mmap()` for zero-copy access to 7 binary column files:
  - `l_shipdate.col` (int32_t) - 239.9 MB
  - `l_quantity.col` (int32_t) - 239.9 MB  
  - `l_extendedprice.col` (int64_t) - 479.9 MB
  - `l_discount.col` (int32_t) - 239.9 MB
