  - `l_returnflag.col` (uint8_t, dictionary-encoded) - 60 MB
  - `l_linestatus.col` (uint8_t, dictionary-encoded) - 60 MB
- Parse dictionary mappings for `l_returnflag` (A, N, R) and `l_linestatus` (F, O)
- Direct array indexing with simple pointer arithmetic instead of parsing
- Use `madvise(MADV_SEQUENTIAL)` for prefetching hints

